
Load Library
```{r}
library(s20x)
success.df = read.table("resVP30.txt", header = TRUE)
success.df$ecc = factor(success.df$ecc)
plot(rate ~ deg, pch = as.character(ecc), data = success.df)
```
```{r}
success.lm = lm(rate ~ deg * ecc, data = success.df)
modcheck(success.lm)
```
```{r}
summary(success.lm)
```
```{r}
anova(success.lm)
```
```{r}
success2.lm = lm(rate ~ deg + ecc, data = success.df)
summary(success2.lm)
```
```{r}
confint(success2.lm)
```
